permissions.name: android.permission.READ_CONTACTS

permissions.description: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways with specific indiv

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS
permissions.label: modify your contacts
permissions.description: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways with specific contacts. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.

permissions.name: com.motorola.audiomonitor.permission.LOCAL
permissions.label: Moto Voice
permissions.description: Allows to access audio hardware

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_CALENDAR
permissions.label: read calendar events plus confidential information
permissions.description: Allows the app to read all calendar events stored on your phone, including those of friends or co-workers. This may allow the app to share or save your calendar data, regardless of confidentiality or sensitivity.

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR
permissions.label: add or modify calendar events and send email to guests without owners' knowledge
permissions.description: Allows the app to add, remove, change events that you can modify on your phone, including those of friends or co-workers. This may allow the app to send messages that appear to come from calendar owners, or modify events without the owners' knowledge.

permissions.name: android.permission.SEND_SMS
permissions.label: send and view SMS messages
permissions.description: Allows the app to send SMS messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.

permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS
permissions.label: receive text messages (SMS)
permissions.description: Allows the app to receive and process SMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_SMS
permissions.label: read your text messages (SMS or MMS)
permissions.description: Allows the app to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. This allows the app to read all SMS messages, regardless of content or confidentiality.

permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_WAP_PUSH
permissions.label: receive text messages (WAP)
permissions.description: Allows the app to receive and process WAP messages. This permission includes the ability to monitor or delete messages sent to you without showing them to you.

permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_MMS
permissions.label: receive text messages (MMS)
permissions.description: Allows the app to receive and process MMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_CELL_BROADCASTS
permissions.label: read cell broadcast messages
permissions.description: Allows the app to read cell broadcast messages received by your device. Cell broadcast alerts are delivered in some locations to warn you of emergency situati

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
permissions.label: read the contents of your SD card
permissions.description: Allows the app to read the contents of your SD card.

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
permissions.label: modify or delete the contents of your SD card
permissions.description: Allows the app to write to the SD card.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION
permissions.label: precise location (GPS and network-based)
permissions.description: Allows the app to get your precise location using the Global Positioning System (GPS) or network location sources such as cell towers and Wi-Fi. These location services must be turned on and available

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
permissions.label: approximate location (network-based)
permissions.description: Allows the app to get your approximate location. This location is derived by location services using network location sources such as cell towers and Wi-Fi. These location services mus

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE
permissions.label: read phone status and identity
permissions.description: Allows the app to access the phone features of the device. This permission allows the app to determine the phone number and device IDs, whether a call is active, and the remote number connected by a call.

permissions.name: android.permission.CALL_PHONE
permissions.label: directly call phone numbers
permissions.description: Allows the app to call phone numbers without your intervention. This may result in unexpected charges or calls. Note that this doesn't allow the app to call emergency numbers. Malicious apps may cost you money by making calls without your confirmation.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_IMS_CALL_SERVICE
permissions.label: access IMS call service
permissions.description: Allows the app to use the IMS service to make calls without your intervention.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG
permissions.label: read call log
permissions.description: Allows the app to read your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. This permission allows apps to save your call log data, and malicious apps may share call log data without your knowledge.

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG
permissions.label: write call log
permissions.description: Allows the app to modify your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.

permissions.name: com.android.voicemail.permission.ADD_VOICEMAIL
permissions.label: add voicemail
permissions.description: Allows the app to add messages to your voicemail inbox.

permissions.name: android.permission.USE_SIP
permissions.label: make/receive SIP calls
permissions.description: Allows the app to make and receive SIP calls.

permissions.name: android.permission.PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS
permissions.label: reroute outgoing calls
permissions.description: Allows the app to see the number being dialed during an outgoing call with the option to redirect the call to a different number or abort the call altogether.

permissions.name: android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO
permissions.label: record audio
permissions.description: Allows the app to record audio with the microphone. This permission allows the app to record audio at any time without your confirmation.

permissions.name: android.permission.CAMERA
permissions.label: take pictures and videos
permissions.description: Allows the app to take pictures and videos with the camera. This permission allows the app to use the camera at any time without your confirmation.

permissions.name: android.permission.BODY_SENSORS
permissions.label: body sensors (like heart rate monitors)
permissions.description: Allows the app to access data from sensors that monitor your physical condition, such as your heart rate.

permissions.name: android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT
permissions.label: use fingerprint hardware
permissions.description: Allows the app to use fingerprint hardware for authentication

permissions.name: com.android.alarm.permission.SET_ALARM
permissions.label: set an alarm
permissions.description: Allows the app to set an alarm in an installed alarm clock app. Some alarm clock apps may not implement this feature.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS
permissions.label: access extra location provider commands
permissions.description: Allows the app to access extra location provider commands. This may allow the app to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.

permissions.name: android.permission.INTERNET
permissions.label: full network access
permissions.description: Allows the app to create network sockets and use custom network protocols. The browser and other applications provide means to send data to the internet, so this permission is not required to send data to the internet.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE
permissions.label: view network connections
permissions.description: Allows the app to view information about network connections such as which networks exist and are connected.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE
permissions.label: view Wi-Fi connections
permissions.description: Allows the app to view information about Wi-Fi networking, such as whether Wi-Fi is enabled and name of connected Wi-Fi devices.

permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE
permissions.label: connect and disconnect from Wi-Fi
permissions.description: Allows the app to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to device configuration for Wi-Fi networks.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_WIMAX_STATE
permissions.label: connect and disconnect from WiMAX
permissions.description: Allows the app to determine whether WiMAX is enabled and information about any WiMAX networks that are connected.

permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIMAX_STATE
permissions.label: Change WiMAX state
permissions.description: Allows the app to connect the phone to and disconnect the phone from WiMAX networks.

permissions.name: android.permission.BLUETOOTH
permissions.label: pair with Bluetooth devices
permissions.description: Allows the app to view the configuration of the Bluetooth on the phone, and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

permissions.name: android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN
permissions.label: access Bluetooth settings
permissions.description: Allows the app to configure the local Bluetooth phone, and to discover and pair with remote devices.

permissions.name: android.permission.NFC
permissions.label: control Near Field Communication
permissions.description: Allows the app to communicate with Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, cards, and readers.

permissions.name: org.simalliance.openmobileapi.SMARTCARD
permissions.label: Access to SIM Card
permissions.description: Allows application to communicate with the SIM card

permissions.name: com.gsma.services.nfc.permission.TRANSACTION_EVENT
permissions.label: NFC Transaction awareness
permissions.description: Allows application to receive information about NFC transaction performed

permissions.name: android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS
permissions.label: find accounts on the device
permissions.description: Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by the phone. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.

permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_MULTICAST_STATE
permissions.label: allow Wi-Fi Multicast reception
permissions.description: Allows the app to receive packets sent to all devices on a Wi-Fi network using multicast addresses, not just your phone. It uses more power than the non-multicast mode.

permissions.name: android.permission.VIBRATE
permissions.label: control vibration
permissions.description: Allows the app to control the vibrator.

permissions.name: android.permission.FLASHLIGHT
permissions.label: control flashlight
permissions.description: Allows the app to control the flashlight.

permissions.name: android.permission.WAKE_LOCK
permissions.label: prevent phone from sleeping
permissions.description: Allows the app to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

permissions.name: android.permission.TRANSMIT_IR
permissions.label: transmit infrared
permissions.description: Allows the app to use the phone's infrared transmitter.

permissions.name: android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS
permissions.label: change your audio settings
permissions.description: Allows the app to modify global audio settings such as volume and which speaker is used for output.

permissions.name: com.motorola.dtv.permission.ACCESS_DTV
permissions.label: Mobile TV
permissions.description: Allow access to control Mobile TV

permissions.name: com.motorola.sensorhub.permission.RAW_STM401
permissions.label: Access to the native SensorHub
permissions.description: Allows direct access to the SensorHub.

permissions.name: com.motorola.sensorhub.permission.ACCESS_SENSOR_HUB
permissions.label: Access to the native SensorHub
permissions.description: Allows direct access to the SensorHub.

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.LOCK_NOW
permissions.label: lock the phone
permissions.description: Allows the app to lock the phone, requiring the user to enter their unlock PIN, password, or pattern in order to resume using the phone.

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.TCMD_LOCAL
permissions.label: Should only be used by Motorola applications to have tcmd permission
permissions.description: Allows app to have gid mot_tcmd

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.ACCESS_HIDDENMENU_DATA
permissions.label: Should only be used by Motorola applications to access HiddenMenu files under /persist/public/hiddenmenu
permissions.description: Allows app to have gid mot_tcmd to read/write the hidden menu files /persist/public/hiddenmenu

permissions.name: android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD
permissions.label: disable your screen lock
permissions.description: Allows the app to disable the keylock and any associated password security. For example, the phone disables the keylock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enables the keylock when the call is finished.

permissions.name: android.permission.GET_TASKS
permissions.label: retrieve running apps
permissions.description: Allows the app to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. This may allow the app to discover information about which applications are used on the device.

permissions.name: android.permission.MANAGE_PROFILE_AND_DEVICE_OWNERS
permissions.label: Manage profile and device owners
permissions.description: Allows apps to set the profile owners and the device owner.

permissions.name: android.permission.REORDER_TASKS
permissions.label: reorder running apps
permissions.description: Allows the app to move tasks to the foreground and background. The app may do this without your input.

permissions.name: android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES
permissions.label: close other apps
permissions.description: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.

permissions.name: android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES
permissions.label: close other apps
permissions.description: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.

permissions.name: android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW
permissions.label: draw over other apps
permissions.description: Allows the app to draw on top of other applications or parts of the user interface. They may interfere with your use of the interface in any application, or change what you think you are seeing in other applications.

permissions.name: android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER
permissions.label: set wallpaper
permissions.description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper.

permissions.name: android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER_HINTS
permissions.label: adjust your wallpaper size
permissions.description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper size hints.

permissions.name: android.permission.SET_TIME_ZONE
permissions.label: set time zone
permissions.description: Allows the app to change the phone's time zone.

permissions.name: android.permission.EXPAND_STATUS_BAR
permissions.label: expand/collapse status bar
permissions.description: Allows the app to expand or collapse the status bar.

permissions.name: com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT
permissions.label: install shortcuts
permissions.description: Allows an application to add Homescreen shortcuts without user intervention.

permissions.name: com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT
permissions.label: uninstall shortcuts
permissions.description: Allows the application to remove Homescreen shortcuts without user intervention.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS
permissions.label: read sync settings
permissions.description: Allows the app to read the sync settings for an account. For example, this can determine whether the People app is synced with an account.

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS
permissions.label: toggle sync on and off
permissions.description: Allows an app to modify the sync settings for an account. For example, this can be used to enable sync of the People app with an account.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS
permissions.label: read sync statistics
permissions.description: Allows an app to read the sync stats for an account, including the history of sync events and how much data is synced.

permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS
permissions.label: modify system settings
permissions.description: Allows the app to modify the system's settings data. Malicious apps may corrupt your system's configuration.

permissions.name: android.permission.PERSISTENT_ACTIVITY
permissions.label: make app always run
permissions.description: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the phone.

permissions.name: android.permission.GET_PACKAGE_SIZE
permissions.label: measure app storage space
permissions.description: Allows the app to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes

permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED
permissions.label: run at startup
permissions.description: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the app to slow down the overall phone by always running.

permissions.name: android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY
permissions.label: send sticky broadcast
permissions.description: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.

permissions.name: android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE
permissions.label: change network connectivity
permissions.description: Allows the app to change the state of network connectivity.

permissions.name: com.motorola.android.permission.USERPREFERREDSIM
permissions.label: Access DualSim Settings
permissions.description: Allows management of dual sim related settings

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.BIND_GEOFENCE_SERVICE
permissions.label: Bind to the Motorola Geofence Service
permissions.description: Allows holder to bind to the Motorola Geofence Service. Should only be used by the system.

permissions.name: android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKAGES
permissions.label: Request install packages
permissions.description: Allows an application to request installation of packages.

permissions.name: android.permission.ACCESS_NOTIFICATION_POLICY
permissions.label: access Do Not Disturb
permissions.description: Allows the app to read and write Do Not Disturb configuration.

permissions.name: android.permission.READ_INSTALL_SESSIONS
permissions.label: Read install sessions
permissions.description: Allows an application to read install sessions. This allows it to see details about active package installations.

permissions.name: android.permission.BIND_CARRIER_SERVICES
permissions.label: bind to carrier services
permissions.description: Allows the holder to bind to carrier services. Should never be needed for normal apps.

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.CLEAR_CACHE
permissions.label: Allows the app to clear cache directory if this directory space is lower than some threshold
permissions.description: Clear Cache

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.READ_CID_BLOCK
permissions.label: Allows an application to read the CID block.
permissions.description: Read cid block

permissions.name: com.motorola.permission.ACCESS_CLOGO_BLOCK
permissions.label: Allows an application to read/write the CLOGO block.
permissions.description: Read/Write clogo block
